---
/* Methodology / Metodología section - 4-step horizontal timeline */
---

<section id="metodologia" class="py-24 bg-brand-800 relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Subtle ambient glow -->
  <div
    class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none opacity-60"
    aria-hidden="true"
    style="background-image: radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 45% at 50% 0%, rgba(245,158,11,0.08), transparent 60%), radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 50% at 50% 100%, rgba(37,99,235,0.12), transparent 60%);"
  ></div>

  <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">

    <!-- Section heading -->
    <div class="text-center fade-in-up">
      <p class="uppercase text-sm tracking-widest font-semibold text-amber-500 mb-3">
        METODOLOGÍA
      </p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
        Un proceso probado para resultados reales
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-16">
        Cuatro pasos que transforman tu área comercial.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Steps timeline -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 relative stagger-children">

      <!-- Connecting horizontal line with gradient (desktop only) -->
      <div
        class="hidden md:block absolute top-8 left-[12.5%] right-[12.5%] h-px"
        style="background-image: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, rgba(22, 58, 107, 0.8) 12%, rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.5) 50%, rgba(22, 58, 107, 0.8) 88%, transparent);"
        aria-hidden="true"
      ></div>

      <!-- Step 1 -->
      <div class="relative z-10 text-center fade-in-up">
        <div class="method-step method-step--accent relative w-16 h-16 rounded-full mx-auto mb-6 flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-bold bg-amber-500 text-brand-800">
          1
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Diagnóstico</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
          Análisis profundo del área comercial actual: equipo, procesos,
          herramientas y métricas.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 2 -->
      <div class="relative z-10 text-center fade-in-up">
        <div class="method-step relative w-16 h-16 rounded-full mx-auto mb-6 flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-bold bg-brand-600 text-white border-2 border-brand-500">
          2
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Estrategia</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
          Plan personalizado con KPIs medibles, alineado a los objetivos de negocio.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 3 -->
      <div class="relative z-10 text-center fade-in-up">
        <div class="method-step relative w-16 h-16 rounded-full mx-auto mb-6 flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-bold bg-brand-600 text-white border-2 border-brand-500">
          3
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Implementación</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
          Ejecución junto al equipo del cliente. No dejamos documentos: dejamos
          resultados.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 4 -->
      <div class="relative z-10 text-center fade-in-up">
        <div class="method-step method-step--accent relative w-16 h-16 rounded-full mx-auto mb-6 flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-bold bg-amber-500 text-brand-800">
          4
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Medición & Ajuste</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
          Monitoreo continuo y corrección en tiempo real para optimizar cada
          acción.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .method-step--accent {
    box-shadow:
      0 0 0 4px rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.12),
      0 8px 24px -8px rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.45);
  }

  .method-step::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: -6px;
    border-radius: 9999px;
    border: 1px dashed rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.25);
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.3s ease-out;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .fade-in-up:hover .method-step::after {
    opacity: 1;
  }
</style>
